(44, 5, 40, 40, 10, 17, 17, NULL, 'Persecution of Apostles', 'Both passages emphasize the persecution faced by the apostles. Acts 5:40 describes the apostles being beaten and commanded not to speak, while Matthew 10:17 warns of being delivered to councils and scourged.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
