(44, 5, 40, 41, 13, 9, 9, NULL, 'Persecution for Speaking Jesus'' Name', 'Both passages emphasize the experience of being beaten and brought before authorities for proclaiming Jesus. Acts 5:40 describes the apostles being beaten and commanded not to speak in Jesus'' name, while Mark 13:9 warns that followers will be beaten and delivered up to councils for His sake.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
